  "text": "Complete FxVanillaOption Type Family Graph across OpenGamma Strata:\n\n## Core Domain Classes (modules/product/)\nThe 4 core Joda-Beans domain classes form the foundation of the type family:\n1. FxVanillaOption (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOption.java) - The base product definition, annotated with @BeanDefinition, implementing FxOptionProduct, Resolvable<ResolvedFxVanillaOption>, ImmutableBean, Serializable.\n2. FxVanillaOptionTrade (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTrade.java) - Trade wrapper with TradeInfo and FxVanillaOption product, implementing FxOptionTrade, ResolvableTrade<ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade>, ImmutableBean, Serializable.\n3. ResolvedFxVanillaOption (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOption.java) - Resolved product form with all adjustments applied, implementing ResolvedProduct, ImmutableBean, Serializable.\n4. ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade.java) - Resolved trade form, implementing ResolvedTrade, ImmutableBean, Serializable.\n\n## Pricer Classes (modules/pricer/)\nStrata supports 2 pricing methods (Black and Vanna-Volga), each with both Trade and Product pricer classes:\n1. BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java) - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade using Black (lognormal) model with BlackFxOptionVolatilities.\n2. BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/BlackFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java) - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using Black model.\n3. VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.java) - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade using Vanna-Volga model with BlackFxOptionSmileVolatilities.\n4. VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer (modules/pricer/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/pricer/fxopt/VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionProductPricer.java) - Prices ResolvedFxVanillaOption using Vanna-Volga model.\n\nNote: The Implied-Tree model is available only for FxSingleBarrierOption, not for FxVanillaOption. A Normal model implementation is not present in this version of Strata.\n\n## Measure Calculation Classes (modules/measure/)\nThe 4 measure calculation classes wire the pricers to the calculation engine:\n1. FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMeasureCalculations.java) - Core measure calculations holding BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer and VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer, computing measures like presentValue, pv01, currencyExposure, currentCash.\n2. FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction.java) - Implements CalculationFunction<FxVanillaOptionTrade>, integrating the trade type with the calculation framework and market data lookup.\n3. FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculations.java) - Public API for vanilla option calculations with DEFAULT instance using BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer and VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer.\n4. FxVanillaOptionMethod (modules/measure/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/measure/fxopt/FxVanillaOptionMethod.java) - Enum implementing NamedEnum and CalculationParameter with two enum constants: BLACK (lognormal model using BlackFxOptionVolatilities) and VANNA_VOLGA (smile model using BlackFxOptionSmileVolatilities).\n\n## Loader Plugin (modules/loader/)\nFxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin (modules/loader/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/loader/csv/FxVanillaOptionTradeCsvPlugin.java) - Implements TradeCsvParserPlugin and TradeCsvWriterPlugin<FxVanillaOptionTrade>, enabling CSV loading/writing of FxVanillaOptionTrade objects. Registered in TradeCsvParserPlugin.ini and TradeCsvWriterPlugin.ini service configuration files.\n\n## Related Classes\nFxSingleBarrierOption (modules/product/src/main/java/com/opengamma/strata/product/fxopt/FxSingleBarrierOption.java) - Barrier option variant that embeds FxVanillaOption as the underlyingOption dependency. This demonstrates the composition relationship where FxVanillaOption serves as a building block for more complex products. Takes FxVanillaOption in its factory methods of(FxVanillaOption underlyingOption, Barrier barrier, CurrencyAmount rebate) and of(FxVanillaOption underlyingOption, Barrier barrier).\n\n## Type Resolution Chain\nThe complete resolution chain follows this pattern:\nFxVanillaOptionTrade -> resolve() -> ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade -> (passed to pricers) -> BlackFxVanillaOptionTradePricer or VannaVolgaFxVanillaOptionTradePricer -> Results (MultiCurrencyAmount, Sensitivities, etc.)\n\nSimilarly for product-level resolution:\nFxVanillaOption -> resolve() -> ResolvedFxVanillaOption -> (passed to product pricers) -> pricing methods\n\nThe measure calculation framework integrates these components through FxVanillaOptionTradeCalculationFunction which:\n1. Accepts FxVanillaOptionTrade targets\n2. Resolves them to ResolvedFxVanillaOptionTrade\n3. Selects the appropriate pricer based on FxVanillaOptionMethod parameter\n4. Computes measures (PRESENT_VALUE, PV01, CURRENCY_EXPOSURE, etc.)\n5. Returns results for all scenarios and measures"
